	<ul>
	<li>Encourage parents to take their children for a walk in their local environment to find a picnic spot, for example, in the woods, at the beach, in a park and so on.</li>
	</ul>


	<h3>Further idea</h3>


	<ul>
	<li>With parental permission, take the children for a walk outdoors to find ideal places to have a picnic.</li>
	</ul>


