	<h3>Support</h3>


	<p>Help the children to cut out the material and to stick it on to their mask.</p>


	<h3>Extension</h3>


	<p>Encourage the children to make raised or padded parts on their masks for the nose or eyes, to give a 3D collage effect.</p>


	<h3>Birth to 36 months</h3>


	<p>Help the children to explore their sense of touch by feeling the range of materials.</p>


	<h3>Cross-curricular links</h3>


	<p><span class="caps">KUW</span> – select the tools and techniques they need to shape, assemble and join materials they are using.</p>


	<p>PD – handle tools, objects, construction and malleable materials safely and with increasing control.</p>

